aspace_helpers.title: Making a shared space for data
we need to import a straggler EAD (C1609)

comments.body:
This is the transformation workflow from the days of the migration (SVN readme):

1. Create container entities from dsc2 and classic containers: 
svn://lib-svn.princeton.edu/libsvn/trunk/rbscXSL/ASpace tools/get-containers.xquery
svn://lib-svn.princeton.edu/libsvn/trunk/rbscXSL/ASpace tools/classic_2_dsc2_containers.xq

2. Transform EADs: 
svn://lib-svn.princeton.edu/libsvn/trunk/rbscXSL/ASpace tools/ASpace_do_containers.xq
svn://lib-svn.princeton.edu/libsvn/trunk/rbscXSL/ASpace tools/ASpace_do_cleanup.xq

3. MUST run after EAD transformation: Extract Agents names_A-F and names_G-Z with get-agent-info-and-delete.xq and delete names, bioghists from EAD;
Remove empty elements with remove-empty-agent-wrappers.xq

4. Create CSV from names_A-F, names_G-Z using names2csv.xq 

5. Validate: svn://lib-svn.princeton.edu/libsvn/trunk/rbscXSL/ASpace tools/validate.xquery (5 min), 
svn://lib-svn.princeton.edu/libsvn/trunk/rbscXSL/ASpace tools/validate-containers.xquery
This is urgent: per Kelly, Dan and Alexis are hoping this can be done this week.
Transformed and imported; Kelly will do some manual cleanup. Closing.
